\v 16 <a name="01000101600004" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">Disse</a>-lhe <a name="01000101600008" ll="SDBH:דָּוִד:000000">Davi</a>: O <a name="01000101600012" ll="SDBH:דָּם:000003">teu</a> <a name="01000101600012" ll="SDBH:דָּם:000003">sangue</a> seja sobre a <a name="01000101600016" ll="SDBH:רֹאשׁ:000000">tua</a> <a name="01000101600016" ll="SDBH:רֹאשׁ:000000">cabeça</a>, porque a <a name="01000101600020" ll="SDBH:פֶּה:000000">tua</a> própria <a name="01000101600020" ll="SDBH:פֶּה:000000">boca</a> <a name="01000101600022" ll="SDBH:ענה:000001">testificou</a> contra ti, <a name="01000101600028" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">dizendo</a>: <a name="01000101600032" ll="SDBH:מות:000001">Matei</a> o <a name="01000101600036" ll="SDBH:מָשִׁיחַ:000000" il="Anoint">ungido</a> do <a name="01000101600038" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>.
    
