\v 35 Então, <a name="01000303500004">veio</a> <a name="01000303500006">todo</a> o <a name="01000303500010" ll="SDBH:עַם:000000">povo</a> <a name="01000303500014" ll="SDBH:ברה:000001">fazer</a> que <a name="01000303500018" ll="SDBH:דָּוִד:000000">Davi</a> comesse <a name="01000303500020" ll="SDBH:לֶחֶם:000000" il="Tandır_bread;tb061116157">pão</a>, sendo <a name="01000303500024">ainda</a> <a name="01000303500028" ll="SDBH:יֹום:000000">dia</a>; porém <a name="01000303500034" ll="SDBH:דָּוִד:000000">Davi</a> <a name="01000303500032" ll="SDBH:שׁבע:000000" il="Oath_Jacob_Esau">jurou</a>, <a name="01000303500038" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">dizendo</a>: Assim me <a name="01000303500042">faça</a> <a name="01000303500046" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000002">Deus</a> o que lhe <a name="01000303500052">aprouver</a>, se eu <a name="01000303500068" ll="SDBH:טעם:000001">provar</a> <a name="01000303500070" ll="SDBH:לֶחֶם:000000">pão</a> ou alguma <a name="01000303500076" ll="SDBH:מְאוּמָה:000000">coisa</a> <a name="01000303500060">antes</a> do <a name="01000303500066" ll="SDBH:שֶׁמֶשׁ:000000" il="Red_sunset;Sun;Sun_pillar;Sunrise;Sunset;Sunset_on_mountain">sol</a> <a name="01000303500062">posto</a>. 
\v 36 Todo o <a name="01000303600008" ll="SDBH:עַם:000000">povo</a> <a name="01000303600010" ll="SDBH:נכר:000000">notou</a> isso e <a name="01000303600014;01000303600018" ll="SDBH:יטב:000006;SDBH:עַיִן:000000">lhe</a> <a name="01000303600014;01000303600018" ll="SDBH:יטב:000006;SDBH:עַיִן:000000">pareceu</a> <a name="01000303600014;01000303600018" ll="SDBH:יטב:000006;SDBH:עַיִן:000000">bem</a>, assim como <a name="01000303600040">lhe</a> <a name="01000303600034;01000303600042" ll="SDBH:טֹוב:000002;SDBH:עַיִן:000000">pareceu</a> <a name="01000303600034;01000303600042" ll="SDBH:טֹוב:000002;SDBH:עַיִן:000000">bem</a> tudo quanto o <a name="01000303600030" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a> <a name="01000303600026">fez</a>. 
\v 37 Todo o <a name="01000303700010" ll="SDBH:עַם:000000">povo</a> e todo o <a name="01000303700016" ll="SDBH:יִשְׂרָאֵל:000000">Israel</a>, naquele mesmo <a name="01000303700022" ll="SDBH:יֹום:000001">dia</a>, <a name="01000303700004">ficaram</a> <a name="01000303700004">sabendo</a> que não procedera do <a name="01000303700038" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a> que <a name="01000303700042" ll="SDBH:מות:000001">matassem</a> a <a name="01000303700046" ll="SDBH:אַבְנֵר:000000">Abner</a>, <a name="01000303700048" ll="SDBH:בֵּן:000000">filho</a> <a name="01000303700050" ll="SDBH:נֵר:001000">de</a> <a name="01000303700050" ll="SDBH:נֵר:001000">Ner</a>. 
