 name="01000602000074" ll="SDBH:רֵיק:000002">qualquer</a>! 
\v 21 <a name="01000602100004" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">Disse</a>, porém, <a name="01000602100006" ll="SDBH:דָּוִד:000000">Davi</a> a <a name="01000602100010" ll="SDBH:מִיכַל:000000">Mical</a>: <a name="01000602100014">Perante</a> o <a name="01000602100016" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>, que me <a name="01000602100020" ll="SDBH:בחר:000000">escolheu</a> a mim antes do que <a name="01000602100026" ll="SDBH:אָב:000000">a</a> <a name="01000602100026" ll="SDBH:אָב:000000">teu</a> <a name="01000602100026" ll="SDBH:אָב:000000">pai</a> e a toda a <a name="01000602100034" ll="SDBH:בַּיִת:000003">sua</a> <a name="01000602100034" ll="SDBH:בַּיִת:000003">casa</a>, <a name="01000602100038" ll="SDBH:צוה:000000">mandando</a>-me que fosse <a name="01000602100042" ll="SDBH:נָגִיד:000000">chefe</a> sobre o <a name="01000602100046" ll="SDBH:עַם:000000">povo</a> do <a name="01000602100048" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>, sobre <a name="01000602100052" ll="SDBH:יִשְׂרָאֵל:000000">Israel</a>, <a name="01000602100060">perante</a> o <a name="01000602100062" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a> <a name="01000602100056" ll="SDBH:שׂחק:000001">me</a> <a name="01000602100056" ll="SDBH:שׂחק:000001">tenho</a> <a name="01000602100056" ll="SDBH:שׂחק:000001">alegrado</a>. 
