\v 23 <a name="01001102300004" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">Disse</a> o <a name="01001102300008" ll="SDBH:מַלְאָךְ:000000">mensageiro</a> a <a name="01001102300012" ll="SDBH:דָּוִד:000000">Davi</a>: Na verdade, aqueles homens <a name="01001102300016" ll="SDBH:גבר:000000">foram</a> <a name="01001102300016" ll="SDBH:גבר:000000">mais</a> <a name="01001102300016" ll="SDBH:גבר:000000">poderosos</a> do que nós e <a name="01001102300026" ll="SDBH:יצא:000000">saíram</a> contra nós ao <a name="01001102300032" ll="SDBH:שָׂדֶה:000000">campo</a>; porém nós fomos contra eles, até à <a name="01001102300042" ll="SDBH:פֶּתַח:000000" il="HK00239;Realia:3.1.2a;Realia:3.1.2b;mat01418">entrada</a> da <a name="01001102300046" ll="SDBH:שַׁעַר:000000" il="CityGate-03-042c;Realia:3.13.3.5b;Tel_Arad">porta</a>. 
