\v 4 <a name="01001200400004">Vindo</a> um <a name="01001200400006" ll="SDBH:הֵלֶךְ:000001">viajante</a> ao <a name="01001200400010">homem</a> <a name="01001200400014" ll="SDBH:עָשִׁיר:000000">rico</a>, <a name="01001200400018" ll="SDBH:חמל:000001">não</a> <a name="01001200400018" ll="SDBH:חמל:000001">quis</a> <a name="01001200400018" ll="SDBH:חמל:000001">este</a> <a name="01001200400022" ll="SDBH:לקח:000000">tomar</a> das <a name="01001200400026" ll="SDBH:צֹאן:000000" il="LB00012;LB00015;LB00017;NBGbs20120208-08;NBGbs20120710-139;NBGpb20140401b;Realia:1.2.1;tb111706002">suas</a> <a name="01001200400026" ll="SDBH:צֹאן:000000" il="LB00012;LB00015;LB00017;NBGbs20120208-08;NBGbs20120710-139;NBGpb20140401b;Realia:1.2.1;tb111706002">ovelhas</a> e do <a name="01001200400032" ll="SDBH:בָּקָר:000000" il="Fauna:2.10;LB00022;tb032905283">gado</a> para <a name="01001200400036">dar</a> <a name="01001200400036">de</a> <a name="01001200400036">comer</a> ao <a name="01001200400042" ll="SDBH:ארח:000000">viajante</a> que <a name="01001200400046">viera</a> a ele; mas <a name="01001200400052" ll="SDBH:לקח:000000">tomou</a> a <a name="01001200400056" ll="SDBH:כִּבְשָׂה:000000" il="Fauna:2.31a;Fauna:2.31c">cordeirinha</a> do <a name="01001200400060">homem</a> <a name="01001200400064" ll="SDBH:רושׁ:000001">pobre</a> e a <a name="01001200400068">preparou</a> para o <a name="01001200400074">homem</a> que lhe havia <a name="01001200400078">chegado</a>. 
\v 5 Então, o <a name="01001200500006" ll="SDBH:אַף:000008">furor</a> de <a name="01001200500008" ll="SDBH:דָּוִד:000000">Davi</a> <a name="01001200500004" ll="SDBH:חרה:000001">se</a> <a name="01001200500004" ll="SDBH:חרה:000001">acendeu</a> <a name="01001200500016" ll="SDBH:מְאֹד:000001">sobremaneira</a> contra aquele <a name="01001200500014">homem</a>, e <a name="01001200500020" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">disse</a> a <a name="01001200500024" ll="SDBH:נָתָן:000001">Natã</a>: Tão certo <a name="01001200500026" ll="SDBH:חַי:000000">como</a> <a name="01001200500026" ll="SDBH:חַי:000000">vive</a> <a name="01001200500028" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">o</a> <a name="01001200500028" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>, o <a name="01001200500038">homem</a> que <a name="01001200500042">fez</a> isso <a name="01001200500032;01001200500034" ll="SDBH:בֵּן:000007;SDBH:מָוֶת:000000">deve</a> <a name="01001200500032;01001200500034" ll="SDBH:בֵּן:000007;SDBH:מָוֶת:000000">ser</a> <a name="01001200500032;01001200500034" ll="SDBH:בֵּן:000007;SDBH:מָוֶת:000000">morto</a>. 
