\v 5 <a name="01001400500004" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">Perguntou</a>-lhe o <a name="01001400500010" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a>: Que tens? Ela <a name="01001400500018" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">respondeu</a>: Ah! <a name="01001400500020" ll="SDBH:אֲבָל:001000">Sou</a> <a name="01001400500022" ll="SDBH:אִשָּׁה:000000">mulher</a> <a name="01001400500024" ll="SDBH:אַלְמָנָה:000000">viúva</a>; <a name="01001400500030" ll="SDBH:מות:000000">morreu</a> <a name="01001400500032">meu</a> <a name="01001400500032">marido</a>. 
