\v 31 Então, <a name="01001503100006" ll="SDBH:נגד:000000" tl="HOTTP1181">fizeram</a> <a name="01001503100006" ll="SDBH:נגד:000000" tl="HOTTP1181">saber</a> a <a name="01001503100004" ll="SDBH:דָּוִד:000000" tl="HOTTP1181">Davi</a>, <a name="01001503100010" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">dizendo</a>: <a name="01001503100012" ll="SDBH:אֲחִיתֹפֶל:000000">Aitofel</a> está entre <a name="01001503100018" ll="SDBH:קשׁר:000008">os</a> <a name="01001503100018" ll="SDBH:קשׁר:000008">que</a> <a name="01001503100018" ll="SDBH:קשׁר:000008">conspiram</a> com <a name="01001503100022" ll="SDBH:אַבְשָׁלֹום:000000">Absalão</a>. Pelo que <a name="01001503100026" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">disse</a> <a name="01001503100028" ll="SDBH:דָּוִד:000000">Davi</a>: Ó <a name="01001503100040" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>, peço-te que <a name="01001503100030" ll="SDBH:סכל:000001">transtornes</a> <a name="01001503100030" ll="SDBH:סכל:000001">em</a> <a name="01001503100030" ll="SDBH:סכל:000001">loucura</a> o <a name="01001503100036" ll="SDBH:עֵצָה:000001">conselho</a> de <a name="01001503100038" ll="SDBH:אֲחִיתֹפֶל:000000">Aitofel</a>. 
