\v 33 <a name="01001503300004" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">Disse</a>-lhe <a name="01001503300008" ll="SDBH:דָּוִד:000000">Davi</a>: Se <a name="01001503300012" ll="SDBH:עבר:000000">fores</a> comigo, ser-me-ás <a name="01001503300024" ll="SDBH:מַשָּׂא:000003">pesado</a>. 
\v 34 Porém, se <a name="01001503400010" ll="SDBH:שׁוב:000023">voltares</a> para a <a name="01001503400008" ll="SDBH:עִיר:000000">cidade</a> e <a name="01001503400014" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">disseres</a> a <a name="01001503400018" ll="SDBH:אַבְשָׁלֹום:000000">Absalão</a>: Eu serei, ó <a name="01001503400026" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a>, <a name="01001503400020" ll="SDBH:עֶבֶד:000000" il="Bolen00049">teu</a> <a name="01001503400020" ll="SDBH:עֶבֶד:000000" il="Bolen00049">servo</a>, como fui, <a name="01001503400040" ll="SDBH:אָז:000001">dantes</a>, <a name="01001503400030" ll="SDBH:עֶבֶד:000000" il="Bolen00049">servo</a> <a name="01001503400032" ll="SDBH:אָב:000000">de</a> <a name="01001503400032" ll="SDBH:אָב:000000">teu</a> <a name="01001503400032" ll="SDBH:אָב:000000">pai</a>, assim, agora, serei <a name="01001503400050" ll="SDBH:עֶבֶד:000000" il="Bolen00049">teu</a> <a name="01001503400050" ll="SDBH:עֶבֶד:000000" il="Bolen00049">servo</a>, <a name="01001503400054" ll="SDBH:פרר:000002">dissipar</a>-me-<a name="01001503400054" ll="SDBH:פרר:000002">ás</a>, então, o <a name="01001503400060" ll="SDBH:עֵצָה:000001">conselho</a> de <a name="01001503400062" ll="SDBH:אֲחִיתֹפֶל:000000">Aitofel</a>. 
