\v 5 <a name="01002100500004" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">Responderam</a> ao <a name="01002100500010" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a>: Quanto ao <a name="01002100500014">homem</a> que <a name="01002100500018" ll="SDBH:כלה:000012">nos</a> <a name="01002100500018" ll="SDBH:כלה:000012">destruiu</a> e <a name="01002100500024" ll="SDBH:דמה:001004">procurou</a> que <a name="01002100500028" ll="SDBH:שׁמד:000000">fôssemos</a> <a name="01002100500028" ll="SDBH:שׁמד:000000">assolados</a>, <a name="01002100500032" ll="SDBH:יצב:000000">sem</a> que pudéssemos <a name="01002100500032" ll="SDBH:יצב:000000">subsistir</a> em <a name="01002100500038" ll="SDBH:גְּבוּל:000000">limite</a> algum de <a name="01002100500040" ll="SDBH:יִשְׂרָאֵל:000000">Israel</a>, 
